<div><div id='zzqdgqij3l10m2nRiverDetailGadget2' class='CRiverDetailGadget-detail CRiverDetailGadget'><div class='controls'><h1>Elkhorn Creek - Forks of Elkhorn US460 Bridge to Knight's Bridge on KY1900 (6 miles)</h1>
<div><div id='zzqdgqij3l10m2nArticleGadget26Container' class='CArticleGadget-view CArticleGadget'><div id='zzqdgqij3l10m2nArticleGadget26-1' class='contents'></div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> <div class='tabcontainer' doLayout='false' id="zzqdgqij3l10m2nContainerView136tabc" dojoType="aw.widget.TabContainer" enableBack="true">
<div id="zzqdgqij3l10m2nContainerView132" trackAsMain='true' class='CContainerView' dojoType="aw.widget.ContentPane" title='RiverMain'>
<div><div id='zzqdgqij3l10m2nRiverMainGadget33' class='CRiverMainGadget-main CRiverMainGadget'>
<div parseWidgets='false' class='nodecoration river-description'>
<table class='nodecoration'>
<tr>
<td>
<h1>Elkhorn Creek, Kentucky, US</h1>
</td>
<td valign=top>
<a href="/content/Wiki/rivers:info:disclaimer/"><img align=right alt=Disclaimer src="/resources/images/disclaimerclick.gif" width=72 height=21></a>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<h2>Forks of Elkhorn US460 Bridge to Knight's Bridge on KY1900 (6 miles) (Elkhorn Gorge)</h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>II(III) (varies with level) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>7.6 Miles </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-3'>
<th>Avg. Gradient</th>
<td>10 fpm</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class='river-photo'>
</div>
<div class='river-break'></div>
